To run in localhost : folow the following steps
1)  download  https://curl.haxx.se/ca/cacert.pem
2) keep it to xampp->php
3) open php.ini
4) find for extension=php_openssl.dll and enable it
5) find for curl.cainfo and assign curl.cainfo=c:\xampp\php\cacert.pem
6) Resatart the server 

It is working for me 

